<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9438</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15820</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比在打篮球。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15820</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21331</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他假装自己是高中篮球队 “老鹰” 里的一员。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21331</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24784</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师在做活动准备。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29021</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“希望活动会有趣。” 波比想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29021</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31995</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他还想继续打篮球。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31995</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36845</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师准备了一盒粉笔和一个球。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36845</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41072</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她吹了吹哨子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41072</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44759</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家都过来吧！” 她喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44759</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49454</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要和莉琪一队！” 尼娜大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49454</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54349</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你还不知道我们要做什么呢。” 波比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54349</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要做一个游戏，叫四方格。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61584</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67396</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比知道四方格游戏，他的姐姐们玩儿过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67396</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70959</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今天的活动一定很有趣。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70959</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75460</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁玩儿过四方格游戏？” 雪莉老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75460</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>只有波比举手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我一定最厉害！” 他想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87991</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“波比，你能帮我们画一个四方格吗？” 雪莉老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87991</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89999</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她拿出粉笔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89999</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96350</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比画了一个大方格，然后把它分成四个小方格。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96350</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105750</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他写上数字1、2、3、4。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105750</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111990</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我一开始把球传给波比。” 雪莉老师说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111990</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120013</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“球必须在我的方格里弹一次才能进入波比的方格。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120013</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124548</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果球碰到线，我就出局了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124548</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132353</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“波比必须用手拍球，让球弹到另外一个方格里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136384</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果他做不到，他就出局。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136384</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144228</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果球弹到大方格外面，没有弹到其他方格里面，他也出局。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144228</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148829</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果他接住了球，他也出局。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148829</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153696</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果波比出局，他就走到1号方格。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153696</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>1号方格的人移到2号方格，以此类推。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167766</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们会玩儿五分钟。最后在4号方格的人就赢了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167766</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174204</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“波比，你在1号方格。莉琪，2号方格。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174204</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182714</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森，3号方格。尼娜，4号方格。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187105</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这不公平！” 波比大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187105</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189487</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会输的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189487</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194191</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是随机安排的，波比。” 雪莉老师回答，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“从4号方格开始。尼娜，给你！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202362</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“准备好了吗？” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202362</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204612</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家点点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204612</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207440</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把球弹给贾森。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207441</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210378</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森把球弹给莉琪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210378</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212946</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪把球弹给波比。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212947</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218205</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比把球弹回给莉琪，但是莉琪没拍到！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218205</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225379</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你出局了！” 波比大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225379</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230275</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“波比，不要大喊大叫。” 雪莉老师对他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230275</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233072</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“尼娜，重新开始吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233072</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246627</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜把球弹给贾森。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246627</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250093</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还剩十秒。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250093</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252132</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比很着急。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他需要让尼娜出局才能赢，但是，没有人把球弹给他！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258851</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“三、二、一。游戏结束。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269427</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！” 波比喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269427</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273419</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“耶，我赢了！” 尼娜大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276372</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“四方格游戏真好玩儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276372</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280724</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“耶，尼娜。” 莉琪欢呼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280724</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288623</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“四方格游戏不公平。” 波比皱着眉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288623</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296413</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“四方格游戏是练习篮球的好方法，不是吗？” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296413</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298905</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比停了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298905</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303191</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。这是练习传球的好方法。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>311505</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师，我们什么时候可以再玩儿一次？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>